stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> IDLE
  IDLE --> PARSING: statement starts
  PARSING --> AST_READY: parse complete
  AST_READY --> MDL_REQUESTED: binding starts
  MDL_REQUESTED --> MDL_WAITING: lock conflict
  MDL_REQUESTED --> MDL_GRANTED: compatible
  MDL_WAITING --> MDL_GRANTED: grant
  MDL_WAITING --> TIMEOUT: lock wait timeout
  MDL_GRANTED --> DICT_PINNED: open DictionaryReadView
  DICT_PINNED --> BINDING: name and type resolution
  BINDING --> BOUND_READY: BoundStatement built
  BOUND_READY --> RELEASED: statement guard closes
  TIMEOUT --> RELEASED: cleanup
  RELEASED --> [*]
